Sure, here are some example sentences in Serbian that use the word "povrede" in different forms and positions:

1. Povrede su najčešći razlog odsustva s posla. (*povrede*) (Injuries are the most common reason for absence from work.)
2. On je zadobio teške *povrede* u saobraćajnoj nesreći. (povrede) (He sustained serious injuries in a car accident.)
3. Lekar je utvrdio da nema ozbiljnih *povreda*. (*povreda*) (The doctor determined that there were no serious injuries.)
4. Ova vrsta sporta nosi visok rizik od *povreda*. (*povreda*) (This type of sport carries a high risk of injuries.)
5. Pored fizičkih *povreda*, žrtve nasilja mogu da pate i od psihičkih posledica. (*povreda*) (In addition to physical injuries, victims of violence may also suffer from psychological consequences.)
6. Zakon o zaštiti prava žrtava nasilja uključuje i naknadu štete za *povrede*. (*povrede*) (The Law on Protection of Victims' Rights also includes compensation for injuries.)
7. Molim vas da mi date povratnu informaciju o *povredi* koju sam prijavio. (*povredi*) (Please give me feedback on the injury I reported.)

